definitions.definition: A former local government district in Buckinghamshire , England , abolished on 31 March 2020 on the creation of Buckinghamshire unitary authority .
A locality in the Maranoa Region, Queensland , Australia .
An unincorporated community in Bucks County , Pennsylvania , United States .
